snippet.title: Sonic Forces Overclocked - Blue Blur Trailer
snippet.description:
The first of a series of trailers to build up to the release of the project, which is projected to release around fall of this year!

Trailer music composed by FoxHunt

Cast: 
Landy as Sonic and Neo Metal Sonic
HyperVoiceActing as Dr Eggman
James Dijit as Infinite

Art Team:
JJsucksalot
Copium V 
AidenEye
Blazetbw
Kacper
Stario

New logo by Clarissa
Animated by Bhis 

Be sure to check out our Twitter for further updates: 
https://twitter.com/SFOverclocked
You can also join the official discord server to talk more about the project: 
https://discord.gg/zasegM3KyQ
